export LANG="${LANG:-en_US.UTF-8}"

export LOGNAME="${LOGNAME:-bhbuilder}"
export USER="${USER:-bhbuilder}"
export HOME="${HOME:-/home/bhbuilder}"
export PATH="${PATH:-/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin:/usr/games:/usr/local/games}"
export SSH_CONNECTION="${SSH_CONNECTION:-172.24.5.99 44312 130.225.212.177 22}"
export XDG_SESSION_ID="${XDG_SESSION_ID:-325576}"
export DISPLAY="${DISPLAY:-:0}"
export _="${_:-./bohrium-by-night/run_benchmark.py}"
export BH_CONFIG=/tmp/bh-job-7d016e49-62e1-4d12-9e72-003af1d2e869.sh_0.config.ini

#SBATCH -J 'Shallow Water'

type = bridge
children = node

children = node

children = node

children = cpu

children = cpu

[range]

impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_filter_range.so
children = cpu
